How can i delete my account?

To delete your NewsBreak account, make sure you have the latest version of NewsBreak from Google Play or the App Store. Sign in to the account you want to delete, go to the 'Me' tab, then 'Edit Profile', and click on the three-dot icon at the upper right corner. You'll see the option 'Delete Account'. For more details, you can check out this article: [How to delete my NewsBreak account](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17775072578573-How-to-delete-my-NewsBreak-account).
how do i delete an organization?

Currently, there isn't a direct option to delete an organization in NewsBreak. If you need assistance with managing or removing an organization, I recommend reaching out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com for further guidance.
